#: ../../source/manual/interfaces.rst:5
msgid ""
"All traffic in OPNsense travels via interfaces. By default, WAN and LAN "
"are assigned, but many more are possible, like GUESTNET (:doc:`captive "
"portal </manual/captiveportal>`) and PFSYNC (:doc:`high availability "
"</manual/hacarp>`)."
